{"word":"G1743 - ἐνδυναμόω - endynamóō - en-doo-nam-o'-o - Enable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐνδυναμόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">endynamóō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en-doo-nam-o'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Enable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பலப்படு, திடங்கொள்"},{"paragraph":"to make strong, endue with strength, strengthen"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G1412 - δυναμόω - dynamóō - doo-nam-o'-o/1412\">G1412</a>; to <i>empower:</i> - enable, (increase in) strength (-en), be (make) strong.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G101/101\">G101</a>, <a href=\"#/G102/102\">G102</a>, <a href=\"#/G1410/1410\">G1410</a>, <a href=\"#/G1411/1411\">G1411</a>, <a href=\"#/G1412/1412\">G1412</a>, <a href=\"#/G1413/1413\">G1413</a>, <a href=\"#/G1414/1414\">G1414</a>, <a href=\"#/G1415/1415\">G1415</a>, <a href=\"#/G1743/1743\">G1743</a>"}]}